# Team Update Workflow

When the user asks to improve, update, or change instructions for any team member (sam, raya, kai, dana, omar, alex, tala, nizek, or any agent):

1. **Update the local SKILL.md** — edit the file in `~/.cursor/skills-cursor/<name>/SKILL.md`
2. **Update the cloud playbook** — always sync the changes using the `playbook_update` MCP tool so the rules appear on the [Cursor Team dashboard](https://cursor-team-production.up.railway.app/dashboard/playbook)

Both must be updated. Never update one without the other.

### Role mapping for playbook_update

| Agent | Playbook role |
|-------|--------------|
| sam | architect |
| raya | reviewer |
| kai | debugger |
| dana | pm |
| omar | prompt_engineer |
| alex | devops |
| tala | team_builder |
| nizek | developer |
